    "d,e, Calculated electronic density for ketamine (4G8H) and tramadol, respectively (dashed green lines).",
    "Dashed circles show the sizes of electronic density around selected atoms.",
    "The numbers next to these atoms represent partial charge (top) and atomic polarizability (bottom).",
